import { Grid, Select, Typography } from "@mui/material"
import { Fragment } from "react"

const Form = () => {

    return (
        <Fragment>
            <Grid container style={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                <Grid item>
                    <Typography variant="h3">포탈 찾기</Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item>
                    <Select></Select>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Fragment>
    )
}

export default Form
